Package de.parsemis.miner.general Description

Contains database and fragment handling.

The graphs that are searched for frequent substructures can be enhanced by a mining algorithm to DataBaseGraphs with spezialized abilities. These are also used to recover the original Graph objects.

The found frequent substructures are represented as Fragments. Each instance of a fragment in the database is represented as an Embedding. There are object-orientated and high performace versions of fragments and embeddings available (for details see de.parsemis.graph).
